{"tid":2323833,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"清純女星轉型遭罵網路妓女「穿白T淋浴」破尺度反擊…2萬人暴動","createTime":"2020-12-13T13:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T19:32:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":57,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ed748a05c5eb35895ac4e8414d25f4be67ddbd","tid":2323833,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"南韓女星林李智（임이지）外型甜美，長相被指神似日星廣末涼子，近年不僅轉型當YouTuber，還開始從清純風格改為性感路線，影片中常常穿著清涼的服裝彈鋼琴，火辣的作風吸引了46萬訂閱，近日透露自己遭到酸民狠罵「網路妓女」，她也拍攝影片反擊，沒想到大尺度的內容累積了超過300萬觀看。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5332/5332069.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5332%2F5332069.jpg&h=14d39d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林李智風格從清純轉變為性感。（圖／翻攝自林李智IG）<br />\n<br />\n林李智經營YouTube頻道「이지Leezy」2年，以穿著性感的服裝彈奏鋼琴聞名，其中一支穿著丁字褲配薄紗、重點部位用胸貼遮起的影片，有高達破400萬次觀看，面對自己火辣的作風，她則淡然地表示「如果我不穿得這麼清涼的話，會有這麼多人看嗎？」態度相當坦蕩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5332/5332080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5332%2F5332080.jpg&h=c35e5d31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林李智風格從清純轉變為性感。（圖／翻攝自林李智IG）<br />\n<br />\n只不過，林李智近日卻在另一個紀錄日常的頻道更新影片，表示自己最近因為點閱率成長感到幸福，卻在某一天收到「停止支付營利收益」的消息，因為穿得太過暴露遭到檢舉，讓她忍不住在鏡頭前含淚，甚至透露自己遭到酸民謾罵「網路妓女」等攻擊性發言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5332/5332072.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5332%2F5332072.jpg&h=5ec2959d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林李智遭到酸民攻擊。（圖／翻攝自林李智IG）<br />\n<br />\n對此，林李智回應被罵「網路妓女」，她反倒覺得沒什麼，自嘲地說道「真慶幸我是網路妓女，比起真正的妓女，網路妓女在體力上不累呢」，接著坦言除了拍攝影片之外，還有兼職烤肉店打工、皮拉提斯講師等，就連演員一職都沒有了想要繼續的動力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5332/5332070.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5332%2F5332070.jpg&h=1ce792e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林李智曬出淋浴影片。（圖／翻攝自林李智IG）<br />\n<br />\n最後，林李智更在影片後半段，公開了一段自己坐在澡盆裡淋浴的畫面，只見她穿著白色緊身上衣坐在紅色的澡盆中，拿起水瓢往身上淋水，雖然鏡頭稍遠，但還是可以看見上衣的材質相當透膚，渾圓雙峰呼之欲出，大尺度的畫面相當引人遐想，而影片一公開後也吸引了超過300萬次觀看，且超過2萬人按讚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5332/5332071.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5332%2F5332071.jpg&h=d04d927e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1388d61a5a215bf951c20316e40f42c4461dcc2d","tid":2323833,"uid":229026,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:09:13.000Z","msg":"嘩痴咗孖筋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5157b822fb82d8b21333cf4fcf9fbb32a5fb09e4","tid":2323833,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1388d61a5a215bf951c20316e40f42c4461dcc2d","tid":2323833,"uid":229026,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:09:13.000Z","msg":"嘩痴咗孖筋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:09:43.000Z","msg":"死女包<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2319500f947f54f25b1b2c2df1b2d2f750c6a3a1","tid":2323833,"uid":166405,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:10:01.000Z","msg":"講事實又唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9932d3c60436ce8afae4d64edd329bb14da08514","tid":2323833,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:11:09.000Z","msg":"太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b34b40504f3de816defca9b62375f5e8e1945d7","tid":2323833,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"9932d3c60436ce8afae4d64edd329bb14da085